### KMP Search API - HTTP Requests
### Use this file with VS Code REST Client extension
### or any .http compatible tool

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5082/api/v1

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5082/api/health

###

### 1. Basic Search - Find "report"
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "report",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 5
}

###

### 2. Partial Word Search - "bud" matches "budget"
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "bud",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 3. Search with Category Filter (Finance only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "policy",
  "filters": {
    "categories": ["Finance"]
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 4. Multi-Filter Search (Categories + Date Range)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "report",
  "filters": {
    "categories": ["Finance", "HR"],
    "dateRange": {
      "from": "2025-01-01",
      "to": "2026-12-31"
    }
  },
  "sort": {
    "field": "relevance",
    "order": "desc"
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20
}

###

### 5. Sort by Date (Newest First)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "annual",
  "sort": {
    "field": "date",
    "order": "desc"
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 6. Sort by Title (Alphabetical)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "policy",
  "sort": {
    "field": "title",
    "order": "asc"
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 7. Pagination - Page 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "annual",
  "page": 2,
  "pageSize": 5
}

###

### 8. Empty Search (All Documents)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 9. Boolean Search - AND Operator
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "budget AND planning",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 10. Boolean Search - OR Operator
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "finance OR budget",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 11. Boolean Search - NEAR Operator
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "annual NEAR report",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 12. Complex Boolean Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "(budget OR planning) AND 2024",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 13. Search by Tag
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "quarterly",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 14. Filter by Multiple Tags (AND logic)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": {
    "tags": ["annual", "2024"]
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###

### 15. Complex Multi-Filter Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "report",
  "filters": {
    "categories": ["Finance", "Legal"],
    "tags": ["annual"],
    "dateRange": {
      "from": "2025-01-01",
      "to": "2026-12-31"
    }
  },
  "sort": {
    "field": "relevance",
    "order": "desc"
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20
}

###

### 16. Autocomplete Suggestions - "bud"
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/suggestions?q=bud&limit=5

###

### 17. Autocomplete Suggestions - "ann"
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/suggestions?q=ann&limit=10

###

### 18. Autocomplete Suggestions - "comp"
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/suggestions?q=comp&limit=10

###

### 19. Autocomplete Suggestions - "sec"
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/suggestions?q=sec&limit=10

###

### 20. Get All Facets
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/facets

###

### 21. Large Page Size (Performance Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 100
}

###

### 22. Error Test - Invalid Suggestions Query (empty q)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/suggestions?q=&limit=5

###

### 23. Search with Invalid Sort Field (should default to relevance)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "budget",
  "sort": {
    "field": "invalid",
    "order": "desc"
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

###
